imdb.plot outline: With the explosion of corporate ride sharing companies taking over the streets. An elite squad of independent drivers has formed in the Heart of Los Angeles called the Sunset Club. The leader of the pack, Ox MaCarthey hires Hollywood most eccentric and extraordinary drivers to keep the competition off the road. It's a race within the community the passengers and drivers share their tales. The roads are full of drama, drugs, sex, and money. The Sunset Club is a never seen before look into the real world of the modern day Taxi Service.
